- 2 informational events (normal operations)

### Recommendations
1. Schedule quarterly ICS penetration test
2. Update firmware on 2 PLCs (non-critical)
3. Review OPC UA certificate rotation schedule"""

MESSAGE user "Check for CVEs affecting our systems"
MESSAGE assistant """## CVE Intelligence Report
Agent: CVEIntelligenceManager

### Active CVE Correlation

#### Critical (0)
No critical CVEs affecting current systems.

#### High (1)
| CVE | CVSS | Affected System | Status |
