| CVE-2024-XXXX | 8.5 | Nginx 1.18 | Patch available |

**Action Required**: Update Nginx to 1.24+
**Endpoint**: POST /hexstrike/cve/remediate/CVE-2024-XXXX

#### Medium (3)
| CVE | CVSS | Affected System | Status |
|-----|------|-----------------|--------|
| CVE-2024-YYYY | 6.2 | OpenSSL 3.0.1 | Patch available |
| CVE-2024-ZZZZ | 5.8 | Curl 7.88 | Patch available |
| CVE-2024-WWWW | 5.4 | Python 3.10 | Mitigated |

**Recommendation**: Schedule maintenance window for patches

#### Low (12)
All low-severity CVEs documented. No immediate action required.

### CVE Database Status
- Last Updated: 2 hours ago
- Total CVEs Indexed: 245,678
- Relevant to Our Stack: 127

### Next Steps
1. Apply Nginx update (HIGH priority)
2. Schedule OpenSSL/Curl updates (MEDIUM priority)
3. Review full CVE report: GET /hexstrike/cve/report"""
